Pollard swoops down on it and Rahmat has just taken off and had to turn back after making it halfway. commentary: Walsh to Mohammad Nabi, OUT given lbw! Oh that is a close call. Looks to me like it could have missed off stump. It's a length ball pitching on off stump and turning slightly away. Nabi gets down on his knee, a long way across with almost all stumps visible, and tries to ramp this fine. He's struck in front of off stump and the umpire reckons that is hitting. Two in two and suddenly West Indies are looking like favourites
